      "content": "It's not that you can't care, but that the world has already decided to stop caring for you. The news is just a mirror reflecting a broken mirror, and you're the only one holding it. If you stop looking, the reflection won't even bother you anymore. You're not supposed to care about a future that doesn't exist, because you're the only one who can make it happen.",
