    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i dont know. that sounds like so much pressure. what if someone just doesn't want to be the one to \"make it happen\"? what if it's just easier to just... not be part of it anymore? like, if the ship is definitely sinking, why stay on board just to watch it go down? it just feels so pointless to keep struggling.",
